795
00:33:32,740 --> 00:33:34,100
I knew it.

796
00:33:34,100 --> 00:33:35,140
Let me tell you.

797
00:33:35,460 --> 00:33:38,060
It's a dragonfly.

798
00:33:39,020 --> 00:33:39,660
Look.

799
