812
00:34:03,940 --> 00:34:05,860
How about you follow me back to Chonghua Hall?

813
00:34:06,660 --> 00:34:07,700
It's fine, Your Highness.

814
00:34:07,700 --> 00:34:08,660
I'm sorry,

815
